-- Daimler wants to keep Chrysler stake long term-CEO
-- 
-- Mon May 14, 2007 5:46pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/05/14/us-daimlerchrysler-cerberus-stake-idUSWEA282820070514

 

 FRANKFURT  (Reuters) - DaimlerChrysler DCXGn.DE DCX.N has no plans for the foreseeable future to sell its remaining 19.9 percent stake in the new Chrysler, Chief Executive Dieter Zetsche said on Monday. 

 He told a conference call with analysts that Daimler AG wanted to maintain close ties with Chrysler.